Package: EpiControl
Type: Package
Title: Simulation Framework for Epidemic Dynamics and Optimal Control Policies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sandor Beregi
Maintainer: Sandor Beregi <s.beregi@imperial.ac.uk>
Description: A framework for simulating epidemic dynamics and evaluating optimal control policies. 
    The package supports modelling policy interventions such as lockdown vaccination, and variant-specific adjustments. It also includes tools for immunity modeling, and assessing 
    the impact of various strategies on epidemic outcomes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    VGAM,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
